trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManagerAsync.XpsSerializationCompleted" /> event of an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManagerAsync" />.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento <see cref="E:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManagerAsync.XpsSerializationCompleted" /> de um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManagerAsync" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to indicate that the serialization was canceled before completion; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> para indicar que a serialização foi cancelada antes da conclusão, caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: A user-supplied object that provides additional data to the event handler.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto fornecido pelo usuário que fornece dados adicionais para o manipulador de eventos.

trans-unit.source: An exception, if any, that interrupted the serialization operation.
trans-unit.target: Uma exceção, se houver, que interrompeu a operação de serialização.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationCompletedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationCompletedEventArgs" />.
